    <body>
        <p>Click the down arrow to open a small window. In this window, you can enter the size of the font in the lower-left field (either type a number or use the up and down arrows). You can select the unit of measurement (e.g., pixels, points, centimeters) using the lower-right drop-down arrow.<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly"> See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Flare/Styles/More/About-UOM-Flare.htm">About Units of Measurement</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Analyzer"> See <MadCap:xref href="../../../../Analyzer/Styles/More/About-UOM-Analyzer.htm">About Units of Measurement</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText> You can return to the default setting by using the upper-right drop-down arrow.</p>
